WEBVTT

10:55.520 --> 10:56.980 line:80%
but I haven't wronged you.

10:57.640 --> 11:00.360 line:80%
People keep dying in your family
these days.

11:00.590 --> 11:03.470 line:80%
Everyone in the lane knows
that you jinxed them!

11:03.470 --> 11:05.920 line:80%
You and Mrs. Song
gossip about me every day.
